Figure 7 Contrast evolution due to the electron-beam-induced deposition in LVSEM images of polymer-sorted 
CNT array obtained by the Inlens detector at a WD of 5 mm during the repeated scan process. (a) The first scan image.

indicate the three rods in (b, c) corresponding to the three peaks in (d). (Zeiss GEMINI)
